                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿تَأْجُرَنِي﴾ تَكُونَ أَجِيرًا لِي فِي رَعْيِ مَاشِيَتِي.</h2>\n<h2>﴿حِجَجٍ﴾ سِنِينَ.</h2>"
        },
        "28": {
            "verses": {
                "28:28": {
                    "id": 28
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿الأَجَلَيْنِ﴾ المُدَّتَيْنِ، الثَّمَانِ أَوِ العَشْرِ.</h2>\n<p>﴿فَلاَ عُدْوَانَ عَلَيَّ﴾ فَلاَ أُطَالَبُ بِزِيَادَةٍ فِي المُدَّةِ.</p>\n<h2>﴿وَكِيلٌ﴾ حَافِظٌ يُرَاقِبُنَا.</h2>"
        },
        "29": {
            "verses": {
                "28:29": {
                    "id": 29
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿آنَسَ﴾ أَبْصَرَ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿جَذْوَةٍ﴾ شُعْلَةٍ مِنَ النَّارِ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿تَصْطَلُونَ﴾ تَسْتَدْفِئُونَ.</h2>"
        },
        "30": {
            "verses": {
                "28:30": {
                    "id": 30
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿شَاطِيءِ﴾ جَانِبِ.</h2>"
        },
        "31": {
            "verses": {
                "28:31": {
                    "id": 31
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿تَهْتَزُّ﴾ تَتَحَرَّكُ، وَتَضْطَرِبُ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿جَآنٌّ﴾ حَيَّةٌ خَفِيفَةٌ فِي سُرْعَةِ حَرَكَتِهَا.</h2>\n<h2>﴿مُدْبِرًا﴾ هَارِبًا جَاعِلاً النَّارَ خَلْفَ ظَهْرِهِ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿وَلَمْ يُعَقِّبْ﴾ لَمْ يَلْتَفِتْ.</h2>"
        },
        "32": {
            "verses": {
                "28:32": {
                    "id": 32
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿اسْلُكْ﴾ أَدْخِلْ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿جَيْبِكَ﴾ فَتْحَةِ قَمِيصِكَ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿مِنْ غَيْرِ سُوءٍ﴾ مِنْ غَيْرِ بَرَصٍ، وَلاَ مَرَضٍ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿وَاضْمُمْ إِلَيْكَ جَنَاحَكَ﴾ ضُمَّ يَدَكَ إِلَى صَدْرِكَ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿مِنَ الرَّهْبِ﴾ لِتَأْمَنَ مِنَ الخَوْفِ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿فَذَانِكَ﴾ هَاتَانِ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿بُرْهَانَانِ﴾ آيَتَانِ.</h2>"
        },
        "33": {
            "verses": {
