            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿أَئِمَّةً﴾ قَادَةً إِلَى النَّارِ.</h2>"
        },
        "42": {
            "verses": {
                "28:42": {
                    "id": 42
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿وَأَتْبَعْنَاهُمْ﴾ أَلْحَقْنَاهُمْ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿لَعْنَةً﴾ طَرْدًا وَإِبْعَادًا مِنَ الرَّحْمَةِ.</h2>\n<p>﴿الْمَقْبُوحِينَ﴾ المُبْعَدِينَ المُسْتَقْذَرَةِ أَفْعَالُهُمْ.</p>"
        },
        "43": {
            "verses": {
                "28:43": {
                    "id": 43
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿الْقُرُونَ الأُولَى﴾ الأُمَمَ المَاضِيَةَ المُكَذِّبَةَ.</h2>\n<p>﴿بَصَائِرَ لِلنَّاسِ﴾ نُورًا لِقُلُوبِهِمْ يُبْصِرُونَ بِهِ الحَقَائِقَ.</p>"
        },
        "44": {
            "verses": {
                "28:44": {
                    "id": 44
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿الْغَرْبِيِّ﴾ الجَبَلِ الغَرْبِيِّ مِنْ مُوسَى عليه السلام.</p>\n<h2>﴿قَضَيْنَا﴾ عَهِدْنَا.</h2>"
        },
        "45": {
            "verses": {
                "28:45": {
                    "id": 45
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿أَنْشَأْنَا﴾ خَلَقْنَا.</h2>\n<h2>﴿قُرُوناً﴾ أُمَمًا.</h2>\n<p>﴿فَتَطَاوَلَ عَلَيْهِمُ الْعُمُرُ﴾ فَمَكَثُوا زَمَنًا طَوِيلاً.</p>\n<h2>﴿ثَاوِيًا﴾ مُقِيمًا.</h2>\n<h2>﴿أَهْلِ مَدْيَنَ﴾ هُمْ قُوْمُ شُعَيْبٍ عليه السلام.</h2>"
        },
        "46": {
            "verses": {
                "28:46": {
                    "id": 46
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿الطُّورِ﴾ جَبَلٍ بِسَيْنَاءَ كَلَّمَ اللهُ مُوسَى عليه السلام بِجَانِبِهِ.</p>"
        },
        "47": {
            "verses": {
                "28:47": {
                    "id": 47
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿تُصِيبَهُمْ مُصِيبَةٌ﴾ يَنْزِلَ بِهِمْ عَذَابٌ.</h2>"
        },
        "48": {
            "verses": {
